{"tid":1928212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國留學生可以點","createTime":"2020-03-16T09:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T17:55:25.000Z","uid":266677,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"384d8612ed287e0677dda7c7a3fc95da0111274e","tid":1928212,"uid":266677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣今年考a level但唔知究竟要唔要返去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多同班同學都話唔返 唔想耽誤學業又話我地學校好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （因為我地學校好偏遠）<br />\n但其他班嘅都好多返曬去<br />\n但宜家機票一票難求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴口罩又俾啲冇腦鬼佬歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但保住自己命仔更加重要<br />\n有冇人同我一樣都煩惱緊<br />\n就黎痴線啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61721adb2c17c0e91d2aeba89c8177ce4ef63d4","tid":1928212,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"你老實講你係咪英國藍絲"},{"pid":"0b49adfaf5ed73d100ed0dac3f0d1beb8f5b8ae7","tid":1928212,"uid":